snippet.title: Project '06 - Demo 2 Release
snippet.description:
A huge continuation to Demo 1 I've been ANXIOUS to release. Happy Halloween!

The demo contains the stages Wave Ocean, Dusty Desert, Radical Train, Flame Core & Kingdom Valley.

(UPDATED TO SILVER RELEASE PATCH V1.1)
Download:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gfyhEh85G5QKNuF5Ai2EdZQDLCpufRRW/view?usp=sharing
Mirrors:

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1dgRVP1A-btVdSVg01263Rtl4MN_K_GIt/view?usp=sharing
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RpsCFqlv_GQGlDfzqXNUOUfsDjXRgDlA/view?usp=sharing

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCEjwges-3BTaWsMwOGJDoGQ
